description:
Eight years ago, a developer who had been using Python2 shared a vivid experience he felt while developing using 2023 Python3 and four new Python3 features he learned.

Idaniel
I love development stories, and I'm interested in all topics about the web, back-end, front-end, and development culture. He is currently a developer at Google in San Francisco, USA.
title: PyCon KR 2023 Python2 Developer's Python3 Development Challenger Idaniel
